items.content_html: algofi-javascript-sdk is the official JavaScript SDK of the Algofi Lending V2 protocol. The SDK supports lending, borrowing, and participating in Algorand Foundation Governance / Consensus via the Algofi Vault. The SDK also provides access to live market analytics. The Python SDKs of all Algofi protocols (V1 Lending, AMM, Governance, Vault) will be migrated to this package.
